title: Grateful Dead Live at Nassau Coliseum on 1993-04-01
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw, They Love Each Other, Minglewood Blues, Candyman, Desolation Row, Stagger Lee, Eternity, Liberty

Set 2

Iko Iko*, Saint Of Circumstance, Crazy Fingers-> Wave To The Wind-> Drums-> Space-> Way To Go Home-> Days Between-> Turn On Your Lovelight, E: Rain

*Barney the dinosaur feigning bass while Phil plays behind the rack
